title: 3D flight simulator
description:
Become a pilot of a passenger plane, go through all the points and get all the stars.

Free flight simulator air over mountainous terrain.
No purchases within the application.
Takeoff and landing of the aircraft.
Flying on a plane over the sea.
Several types of aircraft.
There are views from the cockpit for real aces!
Become a pilot of a passenger plane, go through all the points and get the maximum number of stars.
